verbose_text: Moreover, the results suggested that autophagy was induced concomitantly with the induction of expression of Sirt1 by a moderate stimulus of ox-LDL, suggesting that Sirt1 is involved in autophagy under treatment of ox-LDL to some extent.
evidence: autophagy was induced concomitantly with the induction of expression of Sirt1 by a moderate stimulus of ox-LDL
